      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Luca Metehau</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"/File:LucaMetehau.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/c/cb/LucaMetehau.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"234\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:LucaMetehau.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Luca Metehau <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Luca-Mihnea Metehau</b>, (Luca Metehău)<br />\na Romanian youth chess player, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tenth_grade\">10th grade</a> student at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tudor_Vianu_National_College_of_Computer_Science\">Tudor Vianu National College of Computer Science</a>, participant of national and international Junior <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Olympiad_in_Informatics\">Olympiads in Informatics</a>, and bronze medal winner of the Junior Balkan Olympiad in Informatics in 2019 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nCombining his both passions, Luca Metehau is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/Clover\" title=\"Clover\">Clover</a>, first released in April 2021 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luca_Metehau&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77156\">New engine: Clover</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Metehau</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 23, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luca_Metehau&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/profile/1248090\">Luca-Mihnea Metehau | FIDE profile</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/lucametehau\">lucametehau · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.libertatea.ro/stiri/excelenta-la-14-ani-luca-metehau-olimpicul-la-informatica-pasionat-de-sf-si-inteligenta-artificiala-publicitate-3068126\">Luca Metehău, olimpicul la informatică pasionat de SF și inteligență artificială</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.libertatea.ro/autor/petre-dobrescu\">Petre Dobrescu</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Libertatea\">Libertatea</a>, July 16, 2020 (Romanian)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luca_Metehau&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Image from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.libertatea.ro/stiri/excelenta-la-14-ani-luca-metehau-olimpicul-la-informatica-pasionat-de-sf-si-inteligenta-artificiala-publicitate-3068126\">Luca Metehău, olimpicul la informatică pasionat de SF și inteligență artificială</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.libertatea.ro/autor/petre-dobrescu\">Petre Dobrescu</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Libertatea\">Libertatea</a>, July 16, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://portal.lbi.ro/educatie/rezultate/\">Rezultate la olimpiade si concursuri</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77156\">New engine: Clover</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Metehau</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 23, 2021</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228185809\nCac